# =============================================================================
# This file intentionally has no values.
# =============================================================================
#
# apps/mobile/.env is NOT hand-edited. It's generated by pulling values
# from GCP Secret Manager via:
#
#   npm run env:pull:mobile -- local     # for dev iteration
#   npm run env:pull:mobile -- prod      # for store builds
#
# To set or rotate a single value:
#   npm run env:set:mobile  -- <local|prod> <VAR_NAME>
#
# The full per-mode required-var list lives in apps/mobile/README.md
# and (canonically) in apps/mobile/src/config/env.ts. The pull script
# knows which secrets to fetch per mode.
#
# Both .env and .env.local are gitignored at the repo root and at the
# mobile workspace level — they cannot be committed.
# =============================================================================
